<%- include('layout/header') %>

<div class="inner-container">
    <div class="alert alert-info">
        AI Provider API keys are missing
    </div>
</div>
<div class="inner-container">
    <div class="card">
        <p>To enable AI-powered responses, configure at least one API key from the providers below:</p>

        <ul>
            <li><strong>NEXOS_API_KEY</strong> - For Nexos.ai models</li>
            <li><strong>OPENAI_API_KEY</strong> - For ChatGPT models</li>
            <li><strong>ANTHROPIC_API_KEY</strong> - For Claude models</li>
            <li><strong>GEMINI_API_KEY</strong> - For Gemini models</li>
            <li><strong>XAI_API_KEY</strong> - For xAI models</li>
        </ul>

        <p>
            💡 <strong>Tip:</strong> You can add multiple API keys to access different AI models. Without any provider configured, OpenClaw won't be able to generate responses.
        </p>

        <p style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
            Need help? Check out our <a href="https://www.hostinger.com/support/how-to-install-openclaw-on-hostinger-vps/" target="_blank">setup guide</a> for step-by-step instructions.
        </p>

        <form style="margin-bottom: 0; text-align: center;" method="post" action="/confirm-no-model-keys">
            <button type="submit">Continue Without AI</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</div>

<%- include('layout/footer') %>
